description:
The investment seeks to track the investment results of the Bloomberg Barclays Global Aggregate ex USD 10% Issuer Capped (Hedged) Index composed of global non-U.S. dollar-denominated investment-grade bonds that mitigates exposure to fluctuations between the value of the component currencies and the U.S. dollar.
 The fund generally will invest at least 90% of its assets in the component securities and other instruments of the underlying index. The index measures the performance of the global investment-grade bond market. The fund is non-diversified.
